<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Reload on 瘦了就帅了</title><link>https://blog.cuile.com/tags/reload/</link><description>Recent content in Reload on 瘦了就帅了</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 27 Jun 2026 16:27:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.cuile.com/tags/reload/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>在 Python Shell 中重新导入模块</title><link>https://blog.cuile.com/post/python/python_shell_import_reload/</link><pubDate>Fri, 20 Jan 2023 23:44:17 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://blog.cuile.com/post/python/python_shell_import_reload/</guid><description>&lt;p>不同版本中，不同的表现形式：&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Python 2.x：reload() 是内置函数&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Python 3.0 - 3.3：使用 imp.reload(module)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Python 3.4：imp 已经被废弃，取而代之的是 importlib&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kn">from&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nn">importlib&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kn">import&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">reload&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">reload&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">module&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>参考文档&lt;/p>
